org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.timeline

Class EntityGroupFSTimelineStoreMetrics

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.timeline.EntityGroupFSTimelineStoreMetrics

  • @Metrics(about="Metrics for EntityGroupFSTimelineStore",
         context="yarn")
public class EntityGroupFSTimelineStoreMetrics
extends Object
    This class tracks metrics for the EntityGroupFSTimelineStore. It tracks the read and write metrics for timeline server v1.5. It serves as a complement to TimelineDataManagerMetrics.
